{"tid":1260173,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"灰衣男單野駛乜fact check","createTime":"2019-06-26T18:50:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-26T18:59:46.000Z","uid":34409,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b8c42b6629a2d23cc14d814478613a277ae34dc9","tid":1260173,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T18:50:16.000Z","msg":"現場所有人都見到一個人，拎住件工具衝向警總，意圖引領群眾衝擊警總。<br />\n當時環境既前線示威者，<br />\n邊可能會知道佢係一隻冇帶委任證既黑警。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你諗下過去d 便衣俾人識穿左都係屌住離開，<br />\n但佢冇離開不特止，仲要衝返去警總，<br />\n個意圖其實好明顯。"},{"pid":"1a0102e837185a24e5964145cc49d27378ec7734","tid":1260173,"uid":164496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T18:50:39.000Z","msg":"煲大佢！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d763e75afbb223558545090a6ac08935d411fb32","tid":1260173,"uid":19557,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T18:51:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【事實】灰衫警沒帶委任證衝向警總鐵閘並持起棍狀物件。在場人士一度以為其身份為示威者，幸沒有示威者跟隨。最後總部內警員開閘護送進入。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">其他示威者亦 <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>合 理 懷 疑</strong></span> 該名警員企圖帶動示威者衝擊警總。</span><br />\n<br />\n頭先copy一位巴打 大家請廣傳"},{"pid":"3b63d128f36f06e9097f818ed8495fb5be64f0c1","tid":1260173,"uid":57163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T18:51:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4f2c4442106f3eb954af653fb50e344686288a65","tid":1260173,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T18:58:00.000Z","msg":"如果你唔信灰衫男衝嘅版本，下面依個版本就係事實:<br />\n灰衫男隱藏委任證，手執水撥做武器混入示威者企圖搞事。<br />\n好彩比示威者發現，灰衫男事敗逃回警察總部。"},{"pid":"6771f03540a1c7774bdf4f26b8a3abf61292666e","tid":1260173,"uid":98520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-26T18:59:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1259875/page/6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1259875/page/6</a><br />\n<br />\n入黎睇睇幫手推下,唔該"}]}